data.description: This contemporary townhome offers the space of a single-family home, w/low- maintenance.  The main floor boasts 9 ft ceilings and an open concept living area, dining area, and kitchen space.  There are plenty of cabinets, large island, and granite countertops in the kitchen. Natural light shines throughout. On the second level is a large owner's suite with dual walk-in closets, plus two other spacious bedrooms, and a laundry. The walk-out basement features a finished game room, full bathroom, a study/gym, and ample storage. Low-maintenance living with lawn care included. This townhouse at Blackthorn Estates is surrounded by golf courses and country clubs, and very close to Route 22 and Route 130.
